text:
January 3, 2017 1:58 PM Janet Jackson Welcomes First Baby Boy Eissa 
Welcome to the world, Eissa Al Mana ! 
Janet Jackson and husband Wissam Al Mana welcomed their first child together on Tuesday. 
"Janet Jackson and husband Wissam Al Mana are thrilled to welcome their new son Eissa Al Mana into the world," a rep confirmed the the news to TooFab in a statement. "Janet had a stress-free healthy delivery and is resting comfortably." 
The 50-year-old singer postponed her Unbreakable World Tour in April to focus on her family with Mana. She announced they were expecting their first child together in May. 
"My husband and I are planning our family," she said at the time. "So Iâ€™m going to have to delay the tour." 
Janet and Wissam married in 2012. 
Congrats to the happy couple!
